## Authentication and authorization

### Public routes
```ts
import { Public } from '../core/decorators/public.decorator';

@Public()
@Post('login')
login(@Body() dto: LoginDto) { ... }
```

### Role-based
```ts
@Roles(Role.MASTER)
@Get('admin/report')
getReport() { ... }
```

### Workspace-based
```ts
@WorkspaceRoles(WorkspaceRole.OWNER, WorkspaceRole.EDITOR)
@Put(':id')
update(...) { ... }
```

`WorkspaceRolesGuard` extracts `workspaceId` from `params`, `query`, `body`, or `x-workspace-id` header.

---

## Database (Prisma)

Inject via constructor:
```ts
constructor(private readonly prisma: PrismaService) {}
```

Schema conventions:
```prisma
model Project {
  id          String   @id @default(uuid())
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now()) @map("created_at")
  updatedAt   DateTime @updatedAt @map("updated_at")
  workspaceId String   @map("workspace_id")
  workspace   Workspace @relation(fields: [workspaceId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  @@map("projects")
}
```

Migrations:
- Generate via CLI: `npx prisma migrate dev --name description_in_snake_case`
- Never edit migrations already applied in production

---

## Exports and imports

```ts
// вњ… Named exports only, never default
export class ProjectService { ... }

// вњ… Relative imports within the same module
import { CreateProjectDto } from './dto/create-project.dto';

// вњ… Use shared barrel for global utilities
import { PrismaService } from '../shared';
```

